f real solutions to a real osculating\ninstance has a lower bound depending only on the number of defining flags with\nreal osculation points.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 7 Jul 2013 06:03:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-09"}
