ended sine-kernel of\nDyson's Brownian motion model with $\\beta=2$. Following Donsker's invariance\nprinciple, convergence of noncolliding RWs to the Dyson model is also\ndiscussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 7 Jul 2013 12:01:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Sep 2013 02:10:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 11 Jul 2014 01:21:58 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 20 Dec 2014 02:02:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-03"}
